        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Sabit 0.41$ Giris Mantigi</h3>
        <p>
            PaperPoly, sinyal skoru veya fair value'ya bakmaksizin <strong>her zaman 0.40$ baz fiyat + 0.01$ slippage = 0.41$</strong>
            giris fiyati kullanir. Bu sabit giris fiyati, <strong>kazanc/kayip asimetrisini maksimize eder</strong>:
            kazandiginda +%143.9, kaybettiginde -%100. Bu asimetri sayesinde %41 kazanma orani basabas icin yeterlidir.
        </p>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Hisse Hesabi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// Pozisyon acildiginda:
rawEntry     = 0.40
entryPrice   = rawEntry + Slippage = 0.40 + 0.01 = 0.41
positionSize = max(portfolio.Balance x 0.02, $1)

// Hisse sayisi (kavramsal):
shares = positionSize / entryPrice
// Ornek: $1 / $0.41 = 2.439 hisse
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Resolution Mantigi (Mum Yonu)</h3>
        <p>
            Pozisyon, bir sonraki mumun kapanisinda resolve olur. Karar mekanizmasi son derece basittir:
        </p>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// candle.Close >= candle.Open → mum YESIL → UP kazanir
// candle.Close &lt;  candle.Open → mum KIRMIZI → DOWN kazanir

isUp     = candle.Close >= candle.Open
tradeWon = (direction == UP   && isUp)
        || (direction == DOWN && !isUp)
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Kazanc Hesabi (WIN)</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
outcome   = Win
exitPrice = 1.00   // hisse $1'a resolve olur
fee       = positionSize x TakerFeeRate   // $1 x 0.018 = $0.018
PnL       = (1.00 - entryPrice) / entryPrice x positionSize - fee
          = (1.00 - 0.41) / 0.41 x $1 - $0.018
          = 1.4390 x $1 - $0.018
          = $1.439 - $0.018 = +$1.421
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Kayip Hesabi (LOSS)</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
outcome   = Loss
exitPrice = 0.00   // hisse $0'a resolve olur
PnL       = -positionSize   // tum yatirim kaybedilir
          = -$1.00           // fee kesilmez (zaten sifir)
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Basabas Matematik Ispati</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
// Beklenen deger sifir olacak WR:
WR x NetKazanc = (1-WR) x NetKayip
WR x $1.421 = (1-WR) x $1.00
WR x 1.421 + WR x 1.00 = 1.00
WR x 2.421 = 1.00
WR = 1.00 / 2.421 = 0.4130 = %41.3 (fee dahil)

// Fee'siz: WR = 1.00 / 2.439 = 0.410 = %41.0

// Ornek: %50 WR ile beklenen PnL per trade:
E[PnL] = 0.50 x $1.421 - 0.50 x $1.00 = $0.711 - $0.500 = +$0.211
// Yani her islemde ortalama +$0.211 kar beklenir!
        </pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Compound Growth (Bilesik Buyume) Analizi</h3>
        <p>
            %50 WR varsayimiyla, her islemde bakiyenin %2'si kullanildiginda (en az $1), 50 islem sonrasi
            beklenen bakiye: $50 + (50 x 0.50 x $1.421 - 50 x 0.50 x $1.00) = $50 + $10.53 = <strong>$60.53</strong>.
            Bu %21 buyume demektir. 200 islem sonrasi: ~$50 x 1.21^4 = <strong>$107</strong> (bilesik etkiyle).
        </p>
    </div>

